<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%= @title %> | 裕福招聘</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'frontend', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container header">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="top-bar"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="logo"><%= image_tag 'frontend/logo.png', class: 'img-responsive center-block' %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 poster">
          <%= image_tag 'frontend/poster.jpg', class: 'img-responsive' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <nav id="navbar" class="navbar navbar-inserve">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="navbar-collapse collapse">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
              <% @cities.featured.each do |city| %>
              <li<%= raw(' class="actived"') if @city.try(&:id) == city.id %>><%= link_to city.name, city_path(city, anchor: 'navbar') %></li>
              <% end %>
              <li class="last<%= ' actived' unless @city %>"><%= link_to '更多', more_cities_path(anchor: 'navbar') %></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="content-wrap">
            <%= yield %>
            <div class="row footer">
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center"><hr /></div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                请将简历发送至人力资源部hr@fuka.cc邮箱，并注明相应职位。
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                或进入下列招聘平台，投递简历。
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                <%= link_to '裕福@智联招聘', 'http://company.zhaopin.com/CC162549114.htm', target: '_blank' %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                <%= link_to '裕福@拉勾网', 'http://www.lagou.com/gongsi/67635.html', target: '_blank' %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 text-center mt20">
                © 2015裕福实业投资有限公司 版权所有 京ICP备06060349号-1 京公安网备11010502013050
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'frontend', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  </body>
</html>